      <title>印度石油需求增长将在经历丰收后于 2024 年逐渐减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/oil-demand-growth-in-india-to-taper-in-2024-after-bumper-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着疫情后消费激增的消退，印度这个主要亚洲市场的石油需求增长预计明年将放缓，这与中国经济放缓相呼应，并对价格带来新的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/oil-demand-growth-in-india-to-taper-in-2024-after-bumper-years</guid>
